---
import { Anchor } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="about-section" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center text-center">
  <!-- Background Decor -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
     <!-- Optional local glow if needed, keeping it subtle or removing if it conflicts with global aurora -->
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
         <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border border-white/10 rotate-45">
            <Anchor className="w-8 h-8 text-white -rotate-45" />
         </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Biz Kimiz?</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-light mb-12">
        "Düşünce ve Kitap Topluluğu, entelektüel üretimin tüketimden daha değerli olduğuna inananların limanıdır. 
        Amacımız, fikirlerin çarpıştığı ama asla incitmediği, derinliğin sığlığa galip geldiği bir alan yaratmaktır."
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 border-t border-white/10 pt-12">
          <div>
             <span class="block text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">5K+</span>
             <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Aktif Üye</span>
          </div>
          <div>
             <span class="block text-3xl font-bold text-secondary mb-2">120+</span>
             <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Atölye</span>
          </div>
           <div>
             <span class="block text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">850+</span>
             <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Kitap Analizi</span>
          </div>
           <div>
             <span class="block text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">∞</span>
             <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Fikir</span>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</section>
